{"tid":2487182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"18歲男生藏彈簧刀 香淑嫻先准守行為 後改判更生中心 就定罪判刑上訴遭潘敏琦駁回 亦不批准保釋等候終審法院上訴","createTime":"2021-04-13T11:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T14:18:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"14c009b6a61498577a5972245c8eb45eb7701e0d","tid":2487182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"患有過度活躍症及專注力不足的18歲男生，前年11.11三罷首天被警方搜出藏有彈簧刀，經審訊後被裁定管有違禁武器罪成，裁判官香淑嫻最初准他簽保守行為，未幾卻自言遭辯方誤導，主動提出覆核刑期，改判男生入住更生中心。男生今向高等法院提出定罪及刑罰上訴，遭法官潘敏琦駁回；男生同日向終審法院遞交上訴申請，並向高院申請上訴證書，惟潘官同樣拒絕頒發上訴證書，亦不批准他保釋等候終審法院上訴。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人現時任議員助理。得知結果後難掩失望心情，與母親隔着犯人欄道別，母親不住飲泣，與兒子難捨難離。<br />\n<br />\n代表上訴人的大律師郭憬憲今在庭上陳詞指，涉案彈簧刀在日常生活中容易買到。惟法官潘敏琦卻認為常見不代表一定會買，「我就冇呢啲刀喇」。郭又指一般人未必可判斷有彈簧裝置的刀屬於違禁武器，而且案中關鍵是吳知否有彈簧刀在背囊之中。吳被截查時，警方只問他知否刀有何用，而非問他刀子是否屬他所有。<br />\n<br />\n量刑方面，郭憬憲指即使判上訴人被判接受禁閉式刑罰，他已被還柙16天，已經足夠，希望法庭考慮有條件釋放。另外，吳現時任議員助理，更生中心的考慮已經淡化，他亦已受到足夠教訓。潘官重申，上訴庭已講明要綜合考慮案發時的社會事件，加上吳藏有的彈簧刀一旦落入他人手中，或造成嚴重後果，考慮後決定駁回定罪和判刑上訴。<br />\n<br />\n郭其後為上訴人提出上訴至終審法院，惟潘官認為郭提出的法律觀點早已確立和被運用，不接納其申請，拒絕頒發上訴終院證書，亦拒絕讓吳保釋等候上訴，但提醒他可直接向終院申請上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/OS4ZCRKZR5EFTPYIXLWRMBRH4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2FOS4ZCRKZR5EFTPYIXLWRMBRH4U%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=939fd5e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2FOS4ZCRKZR5EFTPYIXLWRMBRH4U%2F&h=6a44be37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/OS4ZCRKZR5EFTPYIXLWRMBRH4U/</a>"},{"pid":"35a94a9067900d846e53a6656ddf1e29f84b99a5","tid":2487182,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6df63126a888056ba93a8016b38be921689c58b","tid":2487182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a94a9067900d846e53a6656ddf1e29f84b99a5","tid":2487182,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ba736f10a5ebb1e5387bbcd1e4824b9c34019e","tid":2487182,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a953935d09889cef627256e16f117510a76c37e","tid":2487182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"2019 年 11 月 11 日「大三罷」期間，一名中五男學生被指在柴灣藏有一把彈簧刀，經審訊後遭裁定管有違禁武器罪成，判守行為 12 個月。惟之後裁判官香淑嫻主動覆核刑期，改判入更生中心。男學生今（13 日）透過律師，向高院原訟庭提出上訴，要求推翻定罪及減刑。但法官潘敏琦聽取陳詞後，認為男生患過度活躍症「並非參與非法罪行的通行證」，決定駁回申請，維持原判，同時拒絕批出終審法院的上訴許可，以及被告的保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人由大律師郭憬憲代表。郭表示，涉案彈簧刀與一般萬用刀無太大差異，只是多出一個彈簧裝置，相信普通人在日常生活中均會持有一把萬用刀。惟法官聞言反駁，指並非人人都會購買萬用刀，甚至將它帶出街，更自言「我就無呢啲刀啦」。郭另指，沒有證據能證明上訴人知道自己的背囊內藏彈簧刀，即使他知道，當中亦涉及很多可能性，故他不應被定罪。不過，法官指郭不能靠幻想去想像被告的答辯理由，形容其說法是「事後孔明」。<br />\n<br />\n刑期方面，郭認為可判處非監禁式刑罰，而裁判官香淑嫻根本不應主動覆核刑期，且上訴人當時已被還押 10 多天，相信已足夠。惟潘敏琦重申，原審裁判官需要作覆核是因為指郭曾作出錯誤陳述，又指雖然上訴人患過度活躍症，但「並非參與非法罪行的通行證」，不認為本案可判處感化等刑罰，終下令維持原判。在定罪及判期上訴被駁回後，郭隨即以案件涉及重大法律觀點為由，申請往終審法院上訴的許可，又為被告申保釋等候上訴，但均被法官拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%82%A3%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%B4%BB%E8%BA%8D%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E7%94%9F%E8%97%8F%E5%BD%88%E7%B0%A7%E5%88%80%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E7%94%B3%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E5%AE%98-%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%E9%9D%9E%E7%BD%AA%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%E8%AD%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%2582%25A3%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25BA%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%25B0%25A7%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%2582%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25AD%2589%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=653c7b5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%2582%25A3%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25BA%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%25B0%25A7%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%2582%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25AD%2589%2F&h=ba17e82e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%82%A3%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%B4%BB%E8%BA%8D%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E7%94%9F%E8%97%8F%E5%BD%88%E7%B0%A7%E5%88%80%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E7%94%B3%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E5%AE%98-%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%E9%9D%9E%E7%BD%AA%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%E8%AD%89/</a>"},{"pid":"a246c8c34894d29673951c1423c94baaf00be8cd","tid":2487182,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f459d7ee571004189fe1130bc0d6ea0212834ef","tid":2487182,"uid":66002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"香淑嫻兩次想判佢感化都俾手足拒絕咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7576&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11OdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=0dce48e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7576</a>"},{"pid":"f45ff2cef69be6b519b7238c0909e645415c9856","tid":2487182,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed4253fa18868d4730b255f82d90656ab37cfeb","tid":2487182,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dc79ea73ad9a1e7ea98d96961c378fb09a63eb","tid":2487182,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f459d7ee571004189fe1130bc0d6ea0212834ef","tid":2487182,"uid":66002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"香淑嫻兩次想判佢感化都俾手足拒絕咗<img src=\